OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FCumbria United Against Suicide, a new
OL,7,Finitiative, has launched in response
OL,8,Fto the county having the highest
OL,9,Fsuicide rate in England and Wales.
OL,11,FOn average in Cumbria, someone dies by
OL,12,Fsuicide every five days.
OL,14,FThe Chief Executive and founder of the
OL,15,Fcharity Every Life Matters, Chris
OL,16,FWood, says Cumbria's figures are
OL,17,Fshocking: "Cumberland has a suicide
OL,18,Frate almost double the England average.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
