PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,F"In 2024, 66 people died across our
OL,7,Fcounty by suicide, which is the
OL,8,Fequivalent of six full football teams
OL,9,F- almost three times the number of
OL,10,Fpeople who die on our roads. And all
OL,11,Fof these deaths are preventable."
OL,13,FEvery Life Matters claims suicide
OL,14,Fisn't a mental health issue, but
OL,15,Frather a response to changing life
OL,16,Fcircumstances. One in four people will
OL,17,Fhave thoughts about suicide in their
OL,18,Flife, so we shouldn't be afraid to
OL,19,Ftalk about it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
