OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FMr Wood says some key life
OL,7,Fcircumstances that can change include:
OL,9,FHe also says Cumbria has "some
OL,10,Fparticular challenges around access to
OL,11,Fhealth, and particularly mental health
OL,12,Fservices".
OL,14,FSuicide rates are generally increasing
OL,15,Facross the North, which Mr Wood
OL,16,Fthinks, "suggests potentially
OL,17,Fausterity, the cost of living crisis
OL,18,Fand the impact of Covid, is affecting
OL,19,Four northern communities, possibly
OL,20,Fmore than the rest of England."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
