OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FThe charity is now getting the
OL,7,Fcommunity involved in prevention.
OL,8,FThrough the Orange Button Community
OL,9,FScheme, anyone can do training to know
OL,10,Fhow to spot the signs and talk to
OL,11,Fsomeone.
OL,13,FThe free sessions will take place in
OL,14,Fvarious locations across Cumbria over
OL,15,Fthe next 12 months, including:
OL,17,FEvery Life Matters Trainer Nell
OL,18,FChapman told ITV Border: "Saying
OL,19,Fsomething is always better than saying
OL,20,Fnothing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
