PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,F"So if we can be kind of helpfully
OL,7,Fnosy, be curious and find out what it
OL,8,Fis that's really going on for
OL,9,Fsomebody, they're unlikely to tell you
OL,10,Fthat they're having thoughts of
OL,11,Fsuicide immediately, but they may tell
OL,12,Fyou a little bit more about what it is
OL,13,Fthat they're experiencing."
OL,15,FThe face-to-face Suicide Alertness
OL,16,Fsession aims to help participants to:
OL,18,FThe training by experienced suicide
OL,19,Fprevention specialists, also looks to:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
