PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FMany organisations are taking the
OL,7,Fopportunity to train their staff to be
OL,8,Fsuicide aware. The sessions teach the
OL,9,Fart of learning to be curious,
OL,10,Fcompassionate and not judgemental.
OL,12,FOn completion, participants become
OL,13,Fpart of the county-wide Orange Button
OL,14,FCommunity Scheme, creating a network
OL,15,Fof people equipped to support others
OL,16,Fin times of need.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
