FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FRevd Grace Cauldwell, Culture Change
OL,7,FLead for Cumbria Methodist Churches
OL,8,Fattended the first course in Kendal
OL,9,Fand told ITV Border the issue is
OL,10,Fsomething they have been thinking
OL,11,Fabout for our society as well, "How do
OL,12,Fwe build those safe, caring
OL,13,Fcommunities so that everyone's got
OL,14,Fsomewhere safe that they can talk?
OL,16,F"Because it's on all of us to make
OL,17,FCumbria a safe and wonderful place to
OL,18,Fbe. We have seen that intervention, or
OL,19,Finterrupting, that continuum can make
OL,20,Fa huge difference in somebody's life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,F"And actually being able to just say,
OL,7,F'are you okay?' can make a real
OL,8,Fdifference. And we often don't
OL,9,Frecognise the power of that."
OL,11,FThe initiative is about bringing these
OL,12,Fconversations to anywhere where we
OL,13,Fmeet, like at the gym. You don't need
OL,14,Fto be in a doctor's surgery to have a
OL,15,Fconversation about how you are. So
OL,16,Fleisure centres are also getting
OL,17,Finvolved.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
