PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FNina Porter, Communications & Business
OL,7,FEngagement Lead at Every Life Matters,
OL,8,Fadded: "The sporting and fitness
OL,9,Fcommunity is crucial in preventing
OL,10,Fsuicide and facilities like leisure
OL,11,Fcentres are places where people come
OL,12,Ftogether regularly, build
OL,13,Frelationships, which supports their
OL,14,Fphysical and mental wellbeing."
OL,26,@pD@HOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
