PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FGLL, which runs a number of leisure
OL,7,Fcentres in Cumbria, has a poignant
OL,8,Freason their team have wanted to be
OL,9,Finvolved, as Lynn Almond, GLL's
OL,10,FRegional Health and Communities
OL,11,FManager explains, "In 2014, we lost a
OL,12,Fvalued colleague, 27-year-old Ben
OL,13,FOsborne, Assistant Manager at Appleby
OL,14,Fand Penrith Leisure Centres. His death
OL,15,Fhad a profound impact on everyone who
OL,16,Fknew him."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776449466
OL,3,CInitiative to tackle highest suicide
OL,4,Crate in England and Wales launches
OL,6,FThe leisure centres have put many
OL,7,Fstaff members through the training,
OL,8,Frealising that people of all ages and
OL,9,Fbackgrounds use their facilities,
OL,10,Fwhich provides an opportunity to
OL,11,Fsupport more people. Ms Almond
OL,12,Fcontinues, "Having that conversation
OL,13,Fand raising the question around
OL,14,Fsuicide does feel quite frightening,
OL,15,Fand without that knowledge and skill
OL,16,Fto be able to have that conversation,
OL,17,Fit can be quite worrying for people
OL,18,Fand being confident in knowing what to
OL,19,Fdo with the answers."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
